Communication Interfaces
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
The system should be connected to the Internat or LAN.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
The system shall connect with the telephone lines.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
The system shall has a connection with an emergency protocol which is connected
 to a hostpital, police, and fire station.
\end_layout

